---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
---

<section class="relative">
	<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
		<div class="py-12 md:py-20">
			<div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center p-6 rounded-md shadow-xl dark:shadow-none">
				<h2 class="text-4xl md:text-4xl font-bold leading-tighter tracking-tighter mb-4 font-heading">
					加入<span class="text-primary-500">猫头鹰实验室</span>
				</h2>
				<p class="text-xl text-gray-600 dark:text-slate-400">
					让有好奇心的人、天马行空的想法和有趣的问题在此汇聚和激发。<br class="hidden md:inline" />
					一起探索未知，创造未来。
				</p>

				<div class="mt-6">
					<a
						class="btn btn-primary mb-4 sm:mb-0"
						href="#contact"
					>
						<Icon name="tabler:mail" class="w-5 h-5 mr-1 -ml-1.5" /> 联系我们
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
